        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX>, once admitted to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SCU</ENAMEX>, was <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">37.5%</NUMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">12</NUMEX> out of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">32</NUMEX>
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX>) may be taken to suggest that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> might have
