        <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Third</NUMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">10</NUMEX> out of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">32</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> requiring a SCU admission
